    <div class="highlight">
      <p><strong>For Our EU Customers.</strong> This addendum supplements our Privacy Policy and explains how we comply with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) for visitors and customers from the European Economic Area (EEA), United Kingdom, and Switzerland.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
    <p>GetPawsy operates as the data controller for personal data collected through our website. We are a US-based company that ships pet products internationally.</p>
    <div class="contact-box">
      <p><strong>Data Controller:</strong> GetPawsy LLC</p>
      <p><strong>Address:</strong> United States</p>
      <p><strong>GDPR Contact:</strong> gdpr@getpawsy.com</p>
    </div>

    <h2>2. Lawful Bases for Processing (Article 6)</h2>
    <p>We process your personal data under the following lawful bases:</p>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Processing Activity</th>
        <th>Legal Basis</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Order processing and fulfillment</td>
        <td>Performance of contract (Art. 6(1)(b))</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Payment processing</td>
        <td>Performance of contract (Art. 6(1)(b))</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Customer support</td>
