      </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>3. Your Rights Under GDPR</h2>
    <p>As an EU data subject, you have the following rights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Right of Access (Art. 15):</strong> Request a copy of your personal data we hold</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Rectification (Art. 16):</strong> Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Erasure (Art. 17):</strong> Request deletion of your personal data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Restrict Processing (Art. 18):</strong> Limit how we use your data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Data Portability (Art. 20):</strong> Receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Object (Art. 21):</strong> Object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Withdraw Consent:</strong> Withdraw consent at any time for consent-based processing</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise these rights, email us at <strong>gdpr@getpawsy.com</strong>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>

    <h2>4. International Data Transfers</h2>
    <p>Your data is transferred to the United States where our servers are located. We implement appropriate safeguards including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs) approved by the European Commission</li>
      <li>Technical security measures (encryption, secure protocols)</li>
      <li>Data minimization practices</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Automated Decision-Making & AI (Article 22)</h2>
    <p>GetPawsy uses AI-powered systems for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Product Recommendations:</strong> Suggesting products based on browsing and purchase history</li>
      <li><strong>Customer Support (Pawsy AI):</strong> Automated chatbot assistance</li>
      <li><strong>Fraud Detection:</strong> Automated screening of orders for fraud indicators</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These automated systems do not make decisions that produce significant legal effects. You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Opt out of AI-powered personalization</li>
      <li>Request human review of any automated decision</li>
      <li>Receive an explanation of how AI systems work</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Data Protection Officer</h2>
    <p>While not legally required, we have designated a privacy contact to handle GDPR-related inquiries:</p>
    <div class="contact-box">
      <p><strong>Privacy Contact:</strong> gdpr@getpawsy.com</p>
      <p>For GDPR requests, please include "GDPR Request" in your email subject line.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>7. Supervisory Authority</h2>
    <p>You have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority in your EU member state if you believe your rights have been violated. A list of EU Data Protection Authorities is available at the European Data Protection Board website.</p>

    <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account data:</strong> Retained while account is active + 3 years after closure</li>
      <li><strong>Order data:</strong> Retained for 7 years for tax/legal compliance</li>
      <li><strong>Marketing preferences:</strong> Retained until you unsubscribe</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Anonymized after 26 months</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For any GDPR-related questions or to exercise your rights:</p>
    <div class="contact-box">
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> gdpr@getpawsy.com</p>
      <p><strong>Subject Line:</strong> GDPR Request - [Your Request Type]</p>
      <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 30 days</p>
    </div>
